## Description

**Uniqush** is a _free_ and _open source_ software which provides a unified
push service for server-side notification to apps on mobile devices. By running
**uniqush** on server side, you can push notification to any supported mobile
platform. [This story](documentation/intro.html) may help you to understand the
basic idea of uniqush.

The latest news about Uniqush will be posted to our
[blog](http://blog.uniqush.org). Or you can follow us on twitter:
[@uniqush](http://twitter.com/uniqush). 

## Features

- Stand alone server program dedicated to push service, which means you can run
  it on your server.
- Multiple push service supported for popular smart phone platforms including
  android, iOS, etc. And we will support more in the future.
- Simple and unified interface for Apps' server developers. You don't need to
  care about receiver's system, simply send an HTTP request to uniqush server
  and it will do all things for you. 


